# Configuration and Tooling

- The project root contains configuration files for building, linting, formatting, and testing.
- Key files include:
  - [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project dependencies and scripts
  - [tsconfig.base.json](mdc:tsconfig.base.json): Base TypeScript configuration
  - [jest.config.ts](mdc:jest.config.ts): Jest test runner configuration
  - [.eslintrc.json](mdc:.eslintrc.json): ESLint configuration
  - [.prettierrc.json](mdc:.prettierrc.json): Prettier formatting rules
  - [nx.json](mdc:nx.json): NX workspace configuration
  - [project.json](mdc:project.json): Project definitions for NX
